Added software update badge to Command Center (top right corner). Badge shows when vm.dashboardUpdateAvailable is true, features blue gradient with pulsing download icon animation. Clicking badge navigates to Status view. Badge is prominent but non-intrusive, positioned out of the way as requested. Build successful (4.28s). Created SoftwareUpdateBadgeTests.swift with 24 tests covering visibility, positioning, interaction, styling, and real-world scenarios.